@DATABASE "Street Hassle"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Street Hassle"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                               Street Hassle
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49661,182)"}          49661,182
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(49883,255)"}          49883,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         Another one by me since the POKE in ZXAMPoke
                         didn't work.

                         Rastan
@endnode
